Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: molo.usermetadata
Version: 1.0.3
Summary: User metadata to be used with Molo.
Home-page: http://github.com/praekelt/molo.usermetadata
Author: Praekelt Foundation
Author-email: dev@praekelt.com
